            DNAn [CPD:C00039]
PRODUCT     diphosphate [CPD:C00013];
            DNAn+1 [CPD:C00039]
COMMENT     Catalyses template-independent extension of the 3'- end of a DNA strand by one nucleotide at a time. Cannot initiate a chain de novo. Nucleoside may be ribo- or deoxyribo-.
